Monday 2 January 2017 Sibahle and Ayanda s showdown ends in a kiss. Smangele manages to fool GC and Thobile. Mxolisi is convinced he has turned Mondli. Mastermind is shocked when Mxolisi insists they steal the car themselves. Tuesday 3 January 2017 Sma s quest to keep Ayanda in the dark gets trickier and harder to sustain. Mxolisi plays a very dangerous game in trying to test the loyalty of a familiar enemy who s posed as a friend. Wednesday 4 January 2017 Mxolisi is convinced that he&#8217;s turned Mondli into his spy. GC faces the church s disciplinary committee. Mondli is on to Mxolisi and he doesn&#8217;t even know it.